cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI 

This paper is primarily focused on network security and intrusion detection, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The use of SNMP-MIB data and machine learning techniques for detecting network anomalies and attacks is related to network infrastructure (cs.NI) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of different classifiers, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and system and information theory (cs.SI).
